title: Richard Burns Rally [MAC OS X]
description:
I have converted Richard Burns Rally from a windows .exe file to Mac OS X application by Wineskin, hope you like it.

Minimum System Requirements:
CPU: 1.6GHz Processor
RAM: 256MB
GPU: 64MB Video RAM (Must support pixel shader)

Recommended System Requirements:
CPU: 2GHz Processor
RAM: 512MB
GPU: 128MB Video RAM (Must support pixel shader)
